<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Tarifa Reseller · PcComponentes</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --pcc-orange: #ff6600;
    --pcc-dark:   #1a1a2e;
    --pcc-mid:    #16213e;
    --pcc-card:   #0f3460;
    --pcc-accent: #e94560;
    --pcc-text:   #eaeaea;
    --pcc-muted:  #8892a4;
    --pcc-border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    --pcc-green:  #00c896;
    --pcc-yellow: #f9c74f;
    --pcc-red:    #e94560;
    --radius:     10px;
    --sidebar-w:  280px;
  }
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { font-size: 15px; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
    background: var(--pcc-dark);
    color: var(--pcc-text);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ── TOP BAR ── */
  .topbar {
    background: var(--pcc-mid);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--pcc-border);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0 24px; height: 58px; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .topbar-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; text-decoration: none; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .topbar-logo .badge {
    background: var(--pcc-orange); color: #fff;
    font-weight: 800; font-size: .75rem; letter-spacing: .05em;
    padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 5px;
  }
  .topbar-logo span { color: var(--pcc-text); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; }
  .topbar-logo small { color: var(--pcc-muted); font-size: .75rem; }
  .topbar-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .topbar-link { color: var(--pcc-muted); font-size: .82rem; text-decoration: none; transition: color .2s; }
  .topbar-link:hover { color: var(--pcc-orange); }

  /* search bar */
  .search-wrap { flex: 1; max-width: 480px; position: relative; }
  .search-wrap input {
    width: 100%; background: rgba(255,255,255,.07); border: 1px solid var(--pcc-border);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px 14px 8px 38px; color: var(--pcc-text);
    font-size: .88rem; outline: none; transition: border-color .2s;
  }
  .search-wrap input::placeholder { color: var(--pcc-muted); }
  .search-wrap input:focus { border-color: var(--pcc-orange); }
  .search-wrap .ic { position: absolute; left: 11px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); color: var(--pcc-muted); font-size: 1rem; }

  /* view toggle */
  .view-btns { display: flex; gap: 4px; }
  .view-btn {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); border: 1px solid var(--pcc-border);
    color: var(--pcc-muted); border-radius: 6px; padding: 6px 10px;
    cursor: pointer; font-size: 1rem; transition: all .2s;
  }
  .view-btn.active { background: var(--pcc-orange); border-color: var(--pcc-orange); color: #fff; }

  /* ── LAYOUT ── */
  .layout { display: flex; min-height: calc(100vh - 58px); }

  /* ── SIDEBAR ── */
  .sidebar {
    width: var(--sidebar-w); flex-shrink: 0;
    background: var(--pcc-mid); border-right: 1px solid var(--pcc-border);
    padding: 20px 16px; overflow-y: auto; position: sticky;
    top: 58px; height: calc(100vh - 58px);
  }
  .sidebar h3 { font-size: .75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .1em; color: var(--pcc-muted); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .sidebar-section { margin-bottom: 22px; }

  /* margin slider */
  .margin-display { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .margin-pct { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--pcc-orange); }
  .margin-hint { font-size: .72rem; color: var(--pcc-muted); line-height: 1.4; }
  input[type=range] {
    -webkit-appearance: none; width: 100%; height: 6px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.1); border-radius: 3px; outline: none; cursor: pointer;
  }
  input[type=range]::-webkit-slider-thumb {
    -webkit-appearance: none; width: 18px; height: 18px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--pcc-orange); cursor: pointer;
  }

  /* filters */
  select.filter {
    width: 100%; background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); border: 1px solid var(--pcc-border);
    color: var(--pcc-text); border-radius: 7px; padding: 8px 10px; font-size: .84rem;
    outline: none; cursor: pointer; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  select.filter option { background: #1a2340; }

  /* checkboxes */
  .check-label { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: .84rem; cursor: pointer; padding: 4px 0; }
  .check-label input { accent-color: var(--pcc-orange); width: 15px; height: 15px; cursor: pointer; }

  /* margin filter pills */
  .margin-pills { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }
  .mpill {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 6px 10px;
    border-radius: 7px; border: 1px solid var(--pcc-border);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.04); cursor: pointer; font-size: .82rem; transition: all .2s;
  }
  .mpill.active { border-color: var(--pcc-orange); background: rgba(255,102,0,.15); }
  .mpill .dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* sort select */
  #sortSel { width: 100%; }

  /* stats */
  .stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .stat { background: rgba(255,255,255,.05); border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px 10px; }
  .stat .num { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--pcc-orange); }
  .stat .lbl { font-size: .7rem; color: var(--pcc-muted); }

  /* help btn */
  .help-btn {
    width: 100%; background: rgba(255,255,255,.05); border: 1px solid var(--pcc-border);
    color: var(--pcc-muted); border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px; font-size: .82rem;
    cursor: pointer; transition: all .2s; margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .help-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.1); color: var(--pcc-text); }

  /* ── MAIN ── */
  .main { flex: 1; padding: 20px; overflow: hidden; }

  .toolbar {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .result-count { font-size: .82rem; color: var(--pcc-muted); margin-right: auto; }

  .btn {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.07); border: 1px solid var(--pcc-border);
    color: var(--pcc-text); border-radius: 8px; padding: 7px 14px;
    font-size: .83rem; cursor: pointer; transition: all .2s; white-space: nowrap;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
  }
  .btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.12); }
  .btn.primary { background: var(--pcc-orange); border-color: var(--pcc-orange); color: #fff; font-weight: 600; }
  .btn.primary:hover { background: #e05a00; }
  .btn.sel-active { background: rgba(255,102,0,.2); border-color: var(--pcc-orange); color: var(--pcc-orange); }
  .btn.danger { background: rgba(233,69,96,.15); border-color: var(--pcc-accent); color: var(--pcc-accent); }

  /* ── TABLE VIEW ── */
  .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: .82rem; }
  thead th {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.05); text-align: left; padding: 9px 12px;
    color: var(--pcc-muted); font-weight: 600; white-space: nowrap;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--pcc-border); position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 10;
  }
  tbody tr {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--pcc-border); transition: background .15s;
  }
  tbody tr:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.04); }
  tbody tr.selected { background: rgba(255,102,0,.1); }
  td { padding: 8px 12px; vertical-align: middle; }
  .td-name { max-width: 320px; }
  .td-name a { color: var(--pcc-text); text-decoration: none; }
  .td-name a:hover { color: var(--pcc-orange); text-decoration: underline; }
  .td-name .no-link { color: var(--pcc-muted); }
  .badge-top { display: inline-block; background: var(--pcc-yellow); color: #000; border-radius: 4px; padding: 1px 5px; font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 700; margin-right: 4px; }
  .badge-stock { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; font-size: .78rem; }
  .badge-stock .dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; }
  .dot-green { background: var(--pcc-green); }
  .dot-red { background: var(--pcc-red); }
  .price { font-weight: 600; }
  .price-pvpr { color: var(--pcc-muted); text-decoration: line-through; }
  .pct-badge {
    display: inline-block; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .pct-high { background: rgba(0,200,150,.15); color: var(--pcc-green); }
  .pct-mid  { background: rgba(249,199,79,.12); color: var(--pcc-yellow); }
  .pct-low  { background: rgba(233,69,96,.12); color: var(--pcc-red); }
  .pct-neg  { background: rgba(233,69,96,.2); color: var(--pcc-red); }
  .pvp-suggested { color: var(--pcc-orange); font-weight: 600; }
  .check-col { cursor: pointer; }
  .row-check { accent-color: var(--pcc-orange); width: 15px; height: 15px; cursor: pointer; }
  .familia-tag { font-size: .72rem; color: var(--pcc-muted); }
  .marca-badge {
    display: inline-block; background: rgba(255,255,255,.08); color: var(--pcc-text);
    border-radius: 4px; padding: 1px 6px; font-size: .72rem;
  }

  /* ── CARD VIEW ── */
  .cards-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .card {
    background: var(--pcc-mid); border: 1px solid var(--pcc-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 14px; cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform .15s, border-color .15s, box-shadow .15s;
    position: relative;
  }
  .card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); border-color: rgba(255,102,0,.4); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.3); }
  .card.selected { border-color: var(--pcc-orange); background: rgba(255,102,0,.08); }
  .card-top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .card-top .marca-badge { flex-shrink: 0; }
  .card-check { position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 10px; accent-color: var(--pcc-orange); width: 16px; height: 16px; cursor: pointer; }
  .card-name { font-size: .82rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.35; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--pcc-text); min-height: 44px; }
  .card-familia { font-size: .7rem; color: var(--pcc-muted); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .card-prices { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .card-price-block { background: rgba(0,0,0,.2); border-radius: 6px; padding: 6px 8px; }
  .card-price-lbl { font-size: .65rem; color: var(--pcc-muted); margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .card-price-val { font-size: .92rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .card-footer { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .card-link { font-size: .72rem; color: var(--pcc-orange); text-decoration: none; }
  .card-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .card-no-link { font-size: .72rem; color: var(--pcc-muted); }

  /* ── SELECTION BAR ── */
  .sel-bar {
    position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 200;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);
    border-top: 2px solid var(--pcc-orange);
    padding: 12px 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
    transform: translateY(100%); transition: transform .3s; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .sel-bar.visible { transform: translateY(0); }
  .sel-bar .sel-info { flex: 1; }
  .sel-bar .sel-count { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--pcc-orange); }
  .sel-bar .sel-total { font-size: .85rem; color: var(--pcc-muted); }
  .sel-bar .sel-actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; }

  /* ── EMPTY STATE ── */
  .empty {
    text-align: center; padding: 80px 20px; color: var(--pcc-muted);
  }
  .empty .ico { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .empty h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--pcc-text); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .empty p { font-size: .85rem; }

  /* ── MODAL ── */
  .modal-overlay {
    display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,.7);
    z-index: 300; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .modal-overlay.open { display: flex; }
  .modal {
    background: var(--pcc-mid); border: 1px solid var(--pcc-border);
    border-radius: 14px; padding: 28px; max-width: 560px; width: 90%; max-height: 85vh;
    overflow-y: auto; position: relative;
  }
  .modal h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: var(--pcc-orange); }
  .modal-close {
    position: absolute; top: 16px; right: 18px; background: none; border: none;
    color: var(--pcc-muted); font-size: 1.4rem; cursor: pointer;
  }
  .modal-step { display: flex; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .step-num {
    background: var(--pcc-orange); color: #fff; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700;
    font-size: .85rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .step-body h4 { font-size: .9rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .step-body p { font-size: .82rem; color: var(--pcc-muted); line-height: 1.5; }
  .step-body p strong { color: var(--pcc-text); }
  .step-body p em { color: var(--pcc-orange); font-style: normal; }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  .footer {
    background: var(--pcc-mid); border-top: 1px solid var(--pcc-border);
    text-align: center; padding: 14px; font-size: .75rem; color: var(--pcc-muted);
  }
  .footer a { color: var(--pcc-orange); text-decoration: none; }

  /* scroll adjustments when sel-bar is visible */
  .main.bar-visible { padding-bottom: 80px; }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .sidebar { display: none; }
    :root { --sidebar-w: 0px; }
    .topbar { gap: 8px; padding: 0 12px; }
    .search-wrap { max-width: 100%; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- TOP BAR -->
<header class="topbar">
  <a class="topbar-logo" href="https://www.pccomponentes.com/resellers" target="_blank">
    <span class="badge">PC</span>
    <div>
      <span>PcComponentes</span><br>
      <small>Programa Resellers</small>
    </div>
  </a>
  <div class="search-wrap">
    <span class="ic">🔍</span>
    <input type="text" id="searchInput" placeholder="Buscar producto, marca…" autocomplete="off">
  </div>
  <div class="topbar-right">
    <a class="topbar-link" href="https://www.pccomponentes.com/resellers" target="_blank">Programa Resellers ↗</a>
    <div class="view-btns">
      <button class="view-btn active" id="btnTable" title="Vista tabla">☰</button>
      <button class="view-btn" id="btnCards" title="Vista tarjetas">⊞</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- LAYOUT -->
<div class="layout">

  <!-- SIDEBAR -->
  <aside class="sidebar">

    <!-- HOW TO USE -->
    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <button class="help-btn" id="helpBtn">❓ Cómo usar esta tarifa</button>
    </div>

    <!-- MARGIN SLIDER -->
    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <h3>Calculadora de margen</h3>
      <div class="margin-display">
        <span class="margin-pct" id="marginLabel">20%</span>
        <span class="margin-hint" id="marginHint">PVP sugerido = Precio Reseller ÷ 0.80</span>
      </div>
      <input type="range" id="marginSlider" min="0" max="70" value="20" step="1">
    </div>

    <!-- FILTERS -->
    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <h3>Marca</h3>
      <select class="filter" id="marcaFilter">
        <option value="">Todas las marcas</option>
      </select>
    </div>

    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <h3>Categoría</h3>
      <select class="filter" id="catFilter">
        <option value="">Todas las categorías</option>
      </select>
    </div>

    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <h3>Disponibilidad</h3>
      <label class="check-label"><input type="checkbox" id="chkStock"> Solo con stock</label>
      <label class="check-label"><input type="checkbox" id="chkTop"> ⭐ Solo oportunidades top</label>
    </div>

    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <h3>Margen potencial</h3>
      <div class="margin-pills">
        <div class="mpill active" data-mg="all"><span class="dot" style="background:#8892a4"></span>Todos</div>
        <div class="mpill" data-mg="high"><span class="dot dot-green"></span>Alto ≥ 30%</div>
        <div class="mpill" data-mg="mid"><span class="dot" style="background:var(--pcc-yellow)"></span>Medio 15–30%</div>
        <div class="mpill" data-mg="low"><span class="dot dot-red"></span>Bajo &lt; 15%</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <h3>Ordenar</h3>
      <select class="filter" id="sortSel">
        <option value="name">Nombre A→Z</option>
        <option value="priceAsc">Precio: menor a mayor</option>
        <option value="priceDesc">Precio: mayor a menor</option>
        <option value="marginDesc">Margen: mayor a menor</option>
        <option value="stockDesc">Más stock primero</option>
        <option value="topFirst">Oportunidades top primero</option>
      </select>
    </div>

    <!-- STATS -->
    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat"><div class="num" id="statTotal">0</div><div class="lbl">Productos</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="num" id="statTop">0</div><div class="lbl">⭐ Top</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="num" id="statStock">0</div><div class="lbl">Con stock</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="num" id="statBrands">0</div><div class="lbl">Marcas</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </aside>

  <!-- MAIN -->
  <main class="main" id="mainContent">
    <div class="toolbar">
      <span class="result-count" id="resultCount">Cargando…</span>
      <button class="btn" id="exportCsvBtn">⬇ Exportar CSV</button>
      <button class="btn" id="selToggleBtn">☑ Seleccionar</button>
    </div>

    <!-- TABLE -->
    <div id="tableView" class="table-wrap">
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th id="selHeader" style="display:none; width:36px;"></th>
            <th>Producto</th>
            <th>Marca</th>
            <th>Categoría</th>
            <th>PVPR</th>
            <th>PVP Web</th>
            <th>Precio Reseller</th>
            <th>% Ganancia</th>
            <th>PVP Sugerido</th>
            <th>Stock</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody id="tableBody"></tbody>
      </table>
      <div class="empty" id="tableEmpty" style="display:none;">
        <div class="ico">🔍</div>
        <h3>Sin resultados</h3>
        <p>Prueba a ajustar los filtros o la búsqueda</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CARDS -->
    <div id="cardsView" style="display:none;">
      <div class="cards-grid" id="cardsGrid"></div>
      <div class="empty" id="cardsEmpty" style="display:none;">
        <div class="ico">🔍</div>
        <h3>Sin resultados</h3>
        <p>Prueba a ajustar los filtros o la búsqueda</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</div>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer class="footer">
  Tarifa exclusiva para el programa Resellers de PcComponentes ·
  <a href="https://www.pccomponentes.com/resellers" target="_blank">www.pccomponentes.com/resellers</a>
</footer>

<!-- SELECTION BAR -->
<div class="sel-bar" id="selBar">
  <div class="sel-info">
    <div class="sel-count" id="selCount">0 productos seleccionados</div>
    <div class="sel-total" id="selTotal">Precio total estimado (precio Reseller): <strong>0,00 €</strong></div>
  </div>
  <div class="sel-actions">
    <button class="btn danger" id="clearSelBtn">🗑 Limpiar</button>
    <button class="btn primary" id="exportSelBtn">⬇ Exportar selección</button>
    <button class="btn" id="copyLinksBtn">🔗 Copiar links</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- HELP MODAL -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="helpModal">
  <div class="modal">
    <button class="modal-close" id="modalCloseBtn">✕</button>
    <h2>Cómo usar la Tarifa Reseller</h2>
    <div class="modal-step">
      <div class="step-num">1</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h4>Busca y filtra productos</h4>
        <p>Usa la barra de búsqueda para encontrar por nombre o marca. Filtra por <strong>marca, categoría, disponibilidad de stock</strong> o nivel de margen desde el panel izquierdo.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-step">
      <div class="step-num">2</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h4>Calcula tu precio de venta</h4>
        <p>Mueve el slider <strong>Margen objetivo</strong> para fijar el porcentaje que quieres ganar. La columna <em>PVP sugerido</em> se actualiza en tiempo real con el precio al que deberías vender cada producto.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-step">
      <div class="step-num">3</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h4>Identifica las mejores oportunidades</h4>
        <p>Los productos marcados con <strong>⭐ Top</strong> combinan buen margen (≥30%) y stock disponible. Filtra por <em>Solo oportunidades top</em> para verlos de golpe.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-step">
      <div class="step-num">4</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h4>Cambia de vista</h4>
